msgid "#About the micro:bit"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: device.md:4
msgid "![microbit from the front and the back](resources/microbit_front_back.png)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: device.md:7
msgid ""
"The central processing unit (CPU) for the micro:bit is the [Nordic "
"nRF51822](https://www.nordicsemi.com/eng/Products/Bluetooth-Smart-Bluetooth-low-energy/nRF51822)  "
"and it controls all functionality offered by the micro:bit."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: device.md:9
msgid "On board the micro:bit there is already:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: device.md:17
msgid ""
"- a 5 x 5 LED matrix [display](ubit/display.md).  - 2 programmable "
"[buttons](ubit/button.md).  - a 3-axis "
"[accelerometer](ubit/accelerometer.md).  - an [e-compass](ubit/compass.md).  "
"- [Bluetooth](ubit/blemanager.md).  - 20 user controlled [pins](ubit/io.md), "
"with Analog and Digital capabilities.  - [serial](ubit/serial.md) "
"capabilities over USB and the edge connector."
msgstr ""

